      <title>博客编写指南</title>
      <link href="/2025/03/21/blog-use-issue/"/>
      <url>/2025/03/21/blog-use-issue/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="博客编写指南">博客编写指南</h1><h2 id="常用指令">常用指令</h2><h3 id="hexo指令">hexo指令</h3><figure class="highlight coffeescript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">npm</span> install -g hexo-cli<span class="comment"># 安装hexo</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo init<span class="comment"># 初始化hexo</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">npm</span> install<span class="comment"># 构建需要的环境与node_modules</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo server<span class="comment"># 启动服务器</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo g<span class="comment"># 生成静态文件</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo d<span class="comment"># 上传到GitHub</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="string">&quot;Markdown文件名&quot;</span>    <span class="comment"># 生成新的Markdown文件用于新的博文</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo clean                  <span class="comment"># 清理缓存文件</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 删除文章只需要将source中的markdown文件删掉，然后执行 hexo g 即可</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>上传github</strong></p><figure class="highlight nginx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">hexo</span> clean                  <span class="comment"># 清理缓存文件</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo g<span class="comment"># 生成静态文件</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo d<span class="comment"># 上传到GitHub</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>重启hexo</strong></p><figure class="highlight nginx"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">hexo</span> clean                  <span class="comment"># 清理缓存文件</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo g<span class="comment"># 生成静态文件</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo S<span class="comment"># 上传到GitHub</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>注意：在每次修改配置文件后都要执行上面三条语句来重启hexo。</p><p><span class="math display">\[\begin{equation}\label{eq1}e=mc^2\end{equation}\]</span></p><p>著名的质能方程 <span class="math inline">\(\eqref{eq1}\)</span>由爱因斯坦提出 ...</p><figure class="highlight matlab"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">clear</span><br><span class="line">clc</span><br><span class="line">close all</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="遇到的问题解决方案">遇到的问题解决方案</h2><p><ahref="https://blog.csdn.net/yexiaohhjk/article/details/82526604">hexonext主题解决无法显示数学公式</a></p><p><ahref="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_45073562/article/details/120289648">「博客搭建」HexoNext主题配置Mathjax遇到的问题：pandoc exited with code null</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
